Description:
A fine pair of antique Austrian enamel, silver and gold ewers. Each beautifully inset with chunks of semi precious stones. Including amethyst rock crystal and hand diamond cut rock crystal. Each ewer very well executed, hand-hammered and finely hand engraved, and further adorned with a 24-carat gold wash.
Austrian silver, gold and enamel, circa 1900. Marked 925 for silver
Measure: H 9.25&quot;
W 6&quot;
D 5&quot;.
